OL,3,CWelsh and UK governments announce #1m
OL,4,Cfund to tackle River Wye pollution
OL,6,FThe UK and Welsh governments have
OL,7,Fannounced a joint #1 million research
OL,8,Finitiative for the heavily polluted
OL,9,FRiver Wye.
OL,11,FThe river, which runs for 130 miles
OL,12,Ffrom central Wales to the Severn
OL,13,FEstuary, has seen its water quality
OL,14,Fand wildlife drastically decline after
OL,15,Fyears of exposure to agricultural
OL,16,Fpollution, sewage discharges and
OL,17,Fphosphates.
