OL,3,CWelsh and UK governments announce #1m
OL,4,Cfund to tackle River Wye pollution
OL,6,FThe cross-border research programme
OL,7,Fwill investigate the sources of
OL,8,Fpollution and pressures facing the
OL,9,Friver, as well as study the impacts of
OL,10,Fchanging farming practices and land
OL,11,Fmanagement. It will also aim to
OL,12,Fdevelop and then test new ways to
OL,13,Fimprove water quality and examine the
OL,14,Fcause of wildlife decline and water
OL,15,Fflow - the movement and quantity of
OL,16,Fwater which is crucial for habitats
OL,17,Fand species.
