OL,3,CWelsh and UK governments announce #1m
OL,4,Cfund to tackle River Wye pollution
OL,6,FMr Irranca-Davies said: "This is an
OL,7,Fimportant step to protect the River
OL,8,FWye, and we are committed to
OL,9,Fcontinuing to work together to restore
OL,10,Four rivers. This research funding will
OL,11,Fsupport both nature recovery and
OL,12,Fsustainable farming practices to
OL,13,Fimprove the local environment.
